des:
The president is well known for his off the cuff remarks and soundbyte friendly quotes. Whether you find his personality endearing or repulsive, we can all agree that he definitely is entertaining. So let's all step back, take off our partisan hats, and enjoy a hearty chuckle together as we listen to some enjoyable Trump quotes.
